chapter.para:
Requel uses many open source components and data. Apache Xalan and
    Xerces for XML processing; Apache Commons libraries; Proxool Java
    connection pool; the MySQL connector for Java; the Spring Framework;
    Hibernate Java Persistence; the Stanford Parser; the Stanford Named Entity
    Recognizer; Jazzy spell checker; OpenNLP Tools; GNU Trove; WordNet SQL
    builder; WordNet; VerbNet; Extended WordNet; Echo2 Web Framework;
    EchoPointNG;
